  {%- comment -%}FAQ{%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lp-faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
    <div class="lp-faq__inner">
      <div class="lp-faq__head">
        <p class="lp-faq__eyebrow bbi-mono">Common questions</p>
        <h2>What non-profits and charities ask before sending the PO.</h2>
        <p class="lp-faq__cta">Still have a question? <a href="tel:18008359565">Call 1-800-835-9565</a> or <a href="/pages/quote">request a quote</a> and we&rsquo;ll respond in 1 business day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-faq__list">

        <details class="lp-faq-item">
          <summary>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__num">01</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__q">Are non-profits OECM-eligible?</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="lp-faq-item__body">
            <p>Many Ontario non-profits are OECM-eligible, particularly those in the broader public sector &mdash; social services organizations, community health centres, charities that receive provincial or municipal funding, and non-profits that provide government-funded programs. Call us with your organization&rsquo;s name and type and we&rsquo;ll confirm eligibility in five minutes. If you qualify, you can purchase directly without a tender.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="lp-faq-item">
          <summary>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__num">02</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__q">How can we stretch a limited furniture budget?</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="lp-faq-item__body">
            <p>Tell us your per-seat or per-room budget on the quote request. We work across a wide range of commercial-grade suppliers and can spec products that hold up to institutional use at a lower price point than you might expect. We can also mix product lines &mdash; spending more on high-use areas like reception and less on secondary storage or back-office spaces &mdash; to make the budget go further without compromising durability.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="lp-faq-item">
          <summary>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__num">03</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__q">Can we phase delivery across budget cycles?</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="lp-faq-item__body">
            <p>Yes &mdash; phased delivery is common for non-profits managing annual budgets. We can quote the full scope and phase delivery room by room or quarter by quarter. Each phase gets its own PO and invoice so your finance team can track against the right budget period. Lead times stay consistent as long as you confirm the phase dates when the first PO is issued.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="lp-faq-item">
          <summary>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__num">04</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__q">What&rsquo;s included in the quote?</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="lp-faq-item__body">
            <p>Every quote includes a line-item product list with quantities, finishes, and pricing &mdash; no hidden fees. We include delivery to your Ontario location and a furniture layout if you send us a floor plan. Installation is quoted separately; let us know if you want it included. Most quotes come back within one business day of receiving your request.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="lp-faq-item">
          <summary>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__num">05</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__q">What are typical lead times?</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="lp-faq-item__body">
            <p>In-stock items ship in 2&ndash;4 weeks. Custom or made-to-order pieces typically run 8&ndash;12 weeks. Lead times are noted on every quote. For grant-funded projects with hard deadlines, let us know the required delivery date on the quote request and we&rsquo;ll confirm whether it&rsquo;s achievable before you issue the PO.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

